    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help the Noidz escape from Cyberia and see how far you can get in the Jungles of CBG and beyond! High Flyer is an action packed flying experience in endless scroller format. Unlock new characters, items and charge up <br>your Lit &amp; Shroom Meters to boost scores and gain rewards. Avoid obstacles and all the machinations of Dr. Buzzkill and Goons and show off your accomplishments to friends via cool social media functions. Complete Daily Challenges to unlock exclusive gear and avatars for your Trophy Case.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Storyline</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Based on the Krypto Kronic franchise and the Krypto Kronicles books, High Flyer brings a fun experience to users while highlighting the epic tales found in Krypto Kronicles. Dabby and his fellow Noidz have been kidnapped under threat of experimentation by Blade Corp and Dr. Buzzkill. Miraculously, a supernatural occurrence has allowed him to escape and  with the help of some young activists. Now he must navigate various terrains to find his friends and become a true High Flyer!</p>",
